OL,6,FAnne travelled from Wales to the
OL,7,FPegasos clinic near Basel in
OL,8,FSwitzerland to end her life in secret,
OL,9,Fas ITV News UK Editor Paul Brand
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FAn assisted dying clinic in
OL,13,FSwitzerland has helped a British woman
OL,14,Fto die without her family's knowledge,
OL,15,Fdespite promising ITV News it had
OL,16,Fchanged its practices.
