OL,6,FIn January this year, 51-year-old Anne
OL,7,F- whose surname we aren't disclosing -
OL,8,Ftravelled from Wales to the Pegasos
OL,9,Fclinic near Basel to end her life in
OL,10,Fsecret.
OL,12,FDyfed Powys Police says it is
OL,13,Finvestigating the circumstances of her
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,FLast year, ITV News exposed how
OL,17,FPegasos also helped 47-year-old
OL,18,FAlistair Hamilton to die without
OL,19,Ftelling his family.
