OL,6,F"She was one of the healthiest people
OL,7,Fwe know," her sister Delia told me,
OL,8,Fsharing a video of Anne at a climbing
OL,9,Fcentre.
OL,11,FWe met Delia and her brother John at
OL,12,FAnne's home in Wales, where they were
OL,13,Fhaving to pack up her belongings.
OL,15,F"Anyone who loses a child probably
OL,16,Fwants to die and be with them", Delia
OL,17,Ftells me. "But with the right help,
OL,18,Fshe could have got through it."
