OL,6,FInstead, Anne's family and friends
OL,7,Flearned of her intention to die via
OL,8,Fseveral 'goodbye' letters posted to
OL,9,Fthem from Switzerland.
OL,11,FTo Delia, Anne wrote: "Dear Delia, So
OL,12,Fif you're reading this, I am no longer
OL,13,Fhere. I have thought about this long
OL,14,Fand hard and need to find (my son) and
OL,15,Fask him some questions.
OL,17,F"There is nothing you could have done,
OL,18,Fbecause this was my decision to go to
OL,19,FSwitzerland and be in peace... I can't
OL,20,Fkeep going and get older and older
OL,21,Fwithout my son."
