OL,6,FAfter signing her name, Anne added,
OL,7,F"Sorry it's such a short letter, I'm
OL,8,Fnot even sure it will arrive before
OL,9,Fyou hear from someone back home."
OL,11,FDelia did hear from someone else first
OL,12,F- another relative who'd also received
OL,13,Fa letter.
OL,15,F"I didn't know whether to start
OL,16,Fgrieving for her, or to start looking
OL,17,Ffor her, I had no idea," Delia told me.
