OL,6,FHoping that Anne had decided not to go
OL,7,Fthrough with her death after all, the
OL,8,Ffamily traced the postal mark on her
OL,9,Fletters and searched for Swiss clinics
OL,10,Fthat she may have visited in the area.
OL,12,FThey came across ITV News' previous
OL,13,Freporting on Pegasos, and immediately
OL,14,Femailed the organisation to ask if
OL,15,FAnne had visited them.
OL,17,FDelia received an auto-reply, saying
OL,18,Fthe company would respond in due
OL,19,Fcourse but was experiencing "higher
OL,20,Fthan usual demand".
