OL,6,FSpecifically, Mr Habegger promised the
OL,7,FHamiltons that if a person arrived at
OL,8,Ftheir clinic unaccompanied he would
OL,9,Fstand over the patient and dial their
OL,10,Ffamily on speakerphone to check that
OL,11,Fthey were aware of what was about to
OL,12,Fhappen.
OL,14,FYet in Anne's case, no such call
OL,15,Ftranspired.
OL,17,FAlistair's 82-year-old mother, Judith,
OL,18,Fis heartbroken that Pegasos appears to
OL,19,Fhave broken its promise to her.
