OL,6,F"I am extremely angry. I cannot
OL,7,Fbelieve that despite what we were
OL,8,Ftold, Pegasos have acted in the same
OL,9,Fheartless, cruel manner as they did
OL,10,Fwhen Alistair died," she told me.
OL,12,F"I think they are despicable and
OL,13,Fshould no longer be allowed to
OL,14,Foperate."
OL,16,FPegasos is not breaking any law in
OL,17,FSwitzerland, where individuals can
OL,18,Flegally be assisted to end their lives
OL,19,Ffor any reason, as long as they are
OL,20,Fnot being coerced.
